 Problem Statement
Time-Consuming Tasks: Users were spending a significant amount of time on manual processes, such as recreating deals and uploading documents in both System A and System B. These repetitive tasks not only reduced overall productivity but also diverted attention from more valuable activities, hindering efficiency and growth.
Solution
Automated Sync Process: Automated the synchronization process between systems through close collaboration between multiple squads.
Close Collaboration: Successful development through collaboration between Team A and Team B.
Automated Data Transfer: Streamlined data transfer process between System A and System B.
Security Enhancements: Document link generation process protected by CloudFront and WAF rules, ensuring secure access.
Gains
Process Efficiency: Due to the automated process, users' time spent on repetitive tasks is eliminated, resulting in an overall 40% gain.
Technical Security: Improved security measures to protect private data from unauthorized access.
User Productivity: Enhanced user productivity by eliminating repetitive tasks, leading to a more efficient workflow.
Architectural Experience: Valuable experience in managing multiple enterprise-level interactions and data flows.